1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,194
-♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

2
00:00:08,957 --> 00:00:13,025
-Oh, my God.
Oh, I am so dang lucky.

3
00:00:13,025 --> 00:00:14,923
This is what birthdays are
about, huh?

4
00:00:14,923 --> 00:00:17,862
I got my wife.
I got my beautiful son.

5
00:00:17,862 --> 00:00:19,395
Huh? My boy.

6
00:00:19,395 --> 00:00:23,320
Oh, and John,
it is so nice you came. Wow.

7
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:26,162
-Yeah.
Dennis hasn't shut up
all day

8
00:00:26,162 --> 00:00:29,312
about
how his cool young boss was
coming to his birthday party.

9
00:00:29,312 --> 00:00:31,394
-Oh, God. Not all day.
Not all day.

10
00:00:31,394 --> 00:00:33,264
-No. It's true.
It's true.

11
00:00:33,264 --> 00:00:37,579
-You know, I thought
that more people
from the office would be here.

12
00:00:37,579 --> 00:00:40,383
-Oh. Me too.

13
00:00:40,732 --> 00:00:44,701
-Alright,
I'm going to Brandon's.

14
00:00:44,701 --> 00:00:46,768
-Oh. Uh, not yet. Gabriel.

15
00:00:46,768 --> 00:00:50,299
Alright?
We're gonna eat some cake first,
and then you can go off
to Brandon's.

16
00:00:50,299 --> 00:00:51,970
Right? They always
want to go to Brandon's.

17
00:00:51,970 --> 00:00:54,968
-I'm done with this.
I want to go to Brandon's.

18
00:00:54,968 --> 00:00:59,114
-Buddy, it's my birthday,
and I want to have
some cake with my son.

19
00:00:59,114 --> 00:01:00,863
-Why?!

20
00:01:00,863 --> 00:01:03,774
-Because it's my birthday,
pal.
Right?

21
00:01:03,774 --> 00:01:07,638
-Damn you! Damn you!

22
00:01:09,659 --> 00:01:11,426
-Yeah.

23
00:01:12,525 --> 00:01:14,512
Kids, right?
-Yeah.

24
00:01:14,512 --> 00:01:17,683
-Yeah. Yeah, I guess.

25
00:01:17,683 --> 00:01:22,339
-Uh-oh, don't tell me
your boys are little angels
or I'm gonna be jealous.

26
00:01:22,339 --> 00:01:25,802
-Yeah, I think John's
just a little stricter
with our boys than that.

27
00:01:25,802 --> 00:01:29,314
-Our kids would
never get away with that.

28
00:01:33,533 --> 00:01:37,363
Hey, Gabriel.
You're not going to
Brandon's tonight, buddy.

29
00:01:37,363 --> 00:01:39,918
-What?! Why?!

30
00:01:39,918 --> 00:01:43,341
-Because you talked back
to me,
and we don't let that slide
in this house.

31
00:01:43,341 --> 00:01:46,206
-Yes, we do.
-No. No, we don't.

32
00:01:46,206 --> 00:01:48,314
-What the hell's going on?
-Gabriel.

33
00:01:48,314 --> 00:01:50,554
What's going on
is that you're staying home.

34
00:01:50,554 --> 00:01:51,990
That's the end of the story.
Sorry.

35
00:01:51,990 --> 00:01:54,430
-I'm -- I'm going to Brandon's!

36
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:56,636
-Hey.
No, you're not, alright?
Sorry.

37
00:01:56,636 --> 00:01:58,186
-Yes, I am!

38
00:01:58,185 --> 00:02:01,784
-Well, okay.
Well, now I'm pissed.

39
00:02:05,562 --> 00:02:08,630
It's not gonna be a sleepover,
I'll tell you that much.

40
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:09,142
-Yes, it is.

41
00:02:09,142 --> 00:02:12,582
-Well, then,
bring your toothbrush, Mister.

42
00:02:12,582 --> 00:02:16,474
-Hell no.
I won't bring my toothbrush.
-Okay. You win.

43
00:02:16,474 --> 00:02:19,772
Oh, sorry you had to see
that side of me, guys.

44
00:02:19,772 --> 00:02:24,301
-So, John,
are you liking the new job?
-Yeah. It's great.

45
00:02:24,301 --> 00:02:27,463
Everyone's been
really welcoming,
especially Dennis here.

46
00:02:27,463 --> 00:02:31,319
-Oh! Because I like people,
I like people.

47
00:02:34,675 --> 00:02:37,679
-This cake tastes like balls.

48
00:02:37,679 --> 00:02:39,780
-Gabriel.
-What?

49
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:43,622
-We don't say "balls," right?
-There's, like,
jelly in the middle. Yuck.

50
00:02:43,622 --> 00:02:46,640
-Gabriel, it's my favorite cake.
Okay?
We're just being nice.

51
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:49,569
-No! I'm going to Brandon's!
-Hey! Hey!
Stop! Stop it, stop it!

52
00:02:49,569 --> 00:02:51,964
-I'm going to Brandon's!
-Okay, okay, okay.

53
00:02:51,964 --> 00:02:54,025
Dang. I had to put
the parent hat on. Right?

54
00:02:54,025 --> 00:02:57,125
Gabriel, go to your room.
-No!

55
00:02:57,125 --> 00:03:02,440
-Oh! Hey, Gabriel.
Gabriel...go to your room.

56
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,971
-Shut up!
-Okay.

57
00:03:03,971 --> 00:03:07,058
Okay. Well, countdown time.
Right?

58
00:03:07,058 --> 00:03:08,604
'Cause that's
what we do in this house.

59
00:03:08,604 --> 00:03:14,228
Gabriel, you're gonna
go to your room in one...

60
00:03:15,050 --> 00:03:17,498
...two...

61
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:23,742
Please go to your room.
-No!

62
00:03:23,742 --> 00:03:26,725
-Okay. Alright.
That's it. Fine.
Then I'm throwing him
over my shoulder.

63
00:03:26,725 --> 00:03:28,360
Right? 'Cause that's
what you gotta do as a parent.

64
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:31,629
Alright, come on. Come on.
You're going over my shoulder.

65
00:03:31,629 --> 00:03:33,689
Stop it!
You're going over my shoulder.

66
00:03:33,689 --> 00:03:35,090
I'm taking him to his room.

67
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:35,991
I'm sorry
you guys have to see this.

68
00:03:35,991 --> 00:03:37,941
Okay. I can't do it.
I can't! Hey!

69
00:03:37,941 --> 00:03:41,048
Stop it, stop it, stop it!

70
00:03:41,048 --> 00:03:43,195
Stop! Stop!

71
00:03:43,195 --> 00:03:45,173
You know what?
Alright,
I'm throwing him over.

72
00:03:45,173 --> 00:03:47,082
Stand up.
Right? 'Cause I gotta do this.

73
00:03:47,082 --> 00:03:49,107
That's being a parent,
and it's ugly.

74
00:03:49,107 --> 00:03:52,254
Jesus Christ.

75
00:03:54,338 --> 00:03:56,121
God, why are you so big?

76
00:03:56,121 --> 00:03:58,422
-I'm small for my age.
-There's no way.

77
00:03:58,422 --> 00:04:01,119
-What is his age?

78
00:04:01,119 --> 00:04:03,168
-Alright, over the shoulder.

79
00:04:03,168 --> 00:04:05,853
Let's go. Come on.
Okay.

80
00:04:05,853 --> 00:04:08,723
You're going over the shoulder.
Okay.

81
00:04:08,723 --> 00:04:10,341
Alright, you know what?

82
00:04:10,341 --> 00:04:13,493
Da-- Okay, okay.

83
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:18,836
I'm gonna have to hit him
where it hurts.
Right? 

84
00:04:18,836 --> 00:04:21,509
Allowance.
You get none.

85
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:24,742
-I want it.
-Fine.

86
00:04:24,742 --> 00:04:27,207
You can't bargain with that,
right?

87
00:04:27,207 --> 00:04:30,201
And I'm sorry that you
had to see me lay down the law.

88
00:04:30,201 --> 00:04:33,614
-Yeah, I think you just
kind of let him push you around

89
00:04:33,614 --> 00:04:36,849
and ruin your cake a bunch
of times.

90
00:04:37,521 --> 00:04:39,712
That's because...

91
00:04:39,712 --> 00:04:42,737
I didn't want to have to
do what I have to do right now.

92
00:04:42,737 --> 00:04:46,084
This is the ugly side
of parenting.

93
00:04:46,084 --> 00:04:49,343
Alright?
We're doing belt, huh?

94
00:04:49,343 --> 00:04:53,846
Because we have to hold...
-Dennis!

95
00:04:53,846 --> 00:04:56,753
-You're not gonna do the belt.

96
00:04:56,858 --> 00:05:01,673
-This may be, uh,
hard to believe,

97
00:05:01,673 --> 00:05:05,792
but this was not what
I planned on happening today.

98
00:05:05,792 --> 00:05:09,103
-You know what, Dennis?
It's -- I get it.

99
00:05:09,103 --> 00:05:11,267
It's tough being a dad, okay?

100
00:05:11,267 --> 00:05:15,698
Especially for you.
Because your son is gigantic.

101
00:05:15,698 --> 00:05:20,361
Way too big.
He looks like Will Ferrell
in a kid wig.

102
00:05:20,361 --> 00:05:24,949
-Hey! Shut up! You shut up!
-Buddy, buddy...

103
00:05:28,617 --> 00:05:31,607
He's my boss.

104
00:05:33,968 --> 00:05:36,210
Thank you
for saying all that.

105
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:40,622
I'm gonna reprimand him, and --
and I'm gonna take him
to his room. Okay? 

106
00:05:40,622 --> 00:05:42,477
You're going
to your room, bud.

107
00:05:42,477 --> 00:05:45,853
You're going to Brandon's.

108
00:05:45,853 --> 00:05:48,231
-Thank you.
-Okay. Let's go.

109
00:05:48,231 --> 00:05:50,388
-Ow! I'm not ready.
-Bad boy, right?

110
00:05:50,488 --> 00:05:52,918
-Don't push me.
-Don't bump me!

